name: CaptainBNB
description: Our mission is simple: to do our part in unleashing the BNB Chain. The crypto space needs a hero, and Captain BNB is here to answer the call. As a true community takeover, the holders are in control, rallying together to support the most viral memecoin on the BNB Chain this cycle. As a thriving community that truly believes in the mission, we stand to be the number one memecoin on the BNB smartchain.
